{"tid":2115164,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"電腦SSD問題","createTime":"2020-07-19T10:17:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T12:56:03.000Z","uid":303864,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e16723fcd570459f1c5c0f16f0c87102b5db7eb6","tid":2115164,"uid":303864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:17:39.000Z","msg":"話說本身用緊隻好細容量既SSD , ADATA 128gb SSD裝左windows 咁當然冇耐就唔夠用 所以就買多隻ADATA既 1TB M.2 (SX6000 Lite SSD)插主機板打算同時用 M.2個隻淨係攞嚟儲存 但係插完之後發覺完全read唔到隻M.2  <br />\n<br />\n想問係塊M.2唔可以同時用 定係要format/ set up張M.2 因為上網睇好似話要format左先read到但自己又唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我以為插左就用得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />求幫忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1d44bd7120abb73edb61be764f548745784af69","tid":2115164,"uid":15909,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:22:20.000Z","msg":"召喚硬件傳心師"},{"pid":"f5ea9e5ae2792d1b9f95b4703f1cacd10632dbf9","tid":2115164,"uid":78143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:23:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w8qqLJ9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw8qqLJ9.jpg&h=529df556&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"236c8eac2e971cc5f054526d928dd5d81eed3948","tid":2115164,"uid":210274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:23:52.000Z","msg":"咩MB,用左PCIE?"},{"pid":"72459ff8e0b42c83b9cdbbd814c61e83083072a4","tid":2115164,"uid":303864,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"236c8eac2e971cc5f054526d928dd5d81eed3948","tid":2115164,"uid":210274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:23:52.000Z","msg":"咩MB,用左PCIE?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:27:41.000Z","msg":"A