Z","msg":"咩都唔知點幫先<br />\nSATA轉插位先"},{"pid":"f4c58eefd7accb67f8ed3cb176cbbc752ed2af80","tid":2115164,"uid":57633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:31:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2c96261ec5443aa5e5c3d6727c01590b911e062","tid":2115164,"uid":303864,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"397220d36e3f4f1e5fec3964c7850f47ba09c8e5","tid":2115164,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5dad40cdb5ca4e06bee5e9b4be2adf4462db3956","tid":2115164,"uid":303864,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f5ea9e5ae2792d1b9f95b4703f1cacd10632dbf9","tid":2115164,"uid":78143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:23:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w8qqLJ9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw8qqLJ9.jpg&h=529df556&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:28:35.000Z","msg":"底板asrock H310CM-itx 其他配置要嚟做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:31:07.000Z","msg":"咩都唔知點幫先<br />\nSATA轉插位先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:35:51.000Z","msg":"本身sata連緊張128gb 而家加左張m.2 1TB 但電腦read唔到 所以想知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da6678a888baa38514a054d7bcf9979446008146","tid":2115164,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2c96261ec5443aa5e5c3d6727c01590b911e062","tid":2115164,"uid":303864,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"397220d36e3f4f1e5fec3964c7850f47ba09c8e5","tid":2115164,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5dad40cdb5ca4e06bee5e9b4be2adf4462db3956","tid":2115164,"uid":303864,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:28:35.000Z","msg":"底板asrock H310CM-itx 其他配置要嚟做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:31:07.000Z","msg":"咩都唔知點幫先<br />\nSATA轉插位先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:35:51.000Z","msg":"本身sata連緊張128gb 而家加左張m.2 1TB 但電腦read唔到 所以想知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:38:23.000Z","msg":"入BIOS都見唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有啲底板LANE唔夠<br />\nSATA / M.2 / PCI-E會SHARE"},{"pid":"de4ad9743bd39518c7a0a6b812b02b4852441ddb","tid":2115164,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:50:57.000Z","msg":"你係BIOS讀唔到?<br />\nDisk Management見唔到?<br />\n定係純粹未format?<br />\n<br />\n傳心師出動"},{"pid":"94fbf887720f310dbca320525fb4c5b925432320","tid":2115164,"uid":335003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T12:23:30.000Z","msg":"你隻 M.2 本身係  pcle / sata ?<br />\n<br />\n仲有 咩CPU ， 有啲CPU  只支援 sata 嘅 m.2 <br />\n有啲 可以上 pcle 但都有唔同頻寬限制。<br />\n<br />\n呢樣就塊板會寫明同唔同代/級數嘅 cpu 對 M.2 支援嘅影響。 有啲 cpu本身會連 M.2 都唔支援，所以你底板有得插都無用。"},{"pid":"b6b6d544ec5b7f592d9005208c0eb33e58eaf446","tid":2115164,"uid":335003,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"72459ff8e0b42c83b9cdbbd814c61e83083072a4","tid":2115164,"uid":303864,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"236c8eac2e971cc5f054526d928dd5d81eed3948","tid":2115164,"uid":210274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:23:52.000Z","msg":"咩MB,用左PCIE?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:27:41.000Z","msg":"Asus H310CM-itx <br />\n<br />\n即係itx板買到最雞最平個隻 唔係用pcie"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T12:48:38.000Z","msg":"啱啱上網 search 一下樓豬隻 m.2 同塊板<br />\n<br />\n1) 你隻M.2 <span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">係用緊 PCIe</span></span> (gen 3)<br />\n<br />\n2) 你塊板/u 係<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">有支持 PCIe M.2</span></span> ，做 boot disk 都得， 不過最高去到 gen2 嘅速度<br />\n<br />\n3) 你入 bios 睇下佢認唔認到你隻碟， 認唔到應該係接觸不良<br />\n<br />\n4) 如果 bios 有， 而 windows 無。  <span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">係因為你未 format 。</span></span><br />\n硬碟唔係usb咁 即插即用，決定咗用咩 format 先會見到。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我覺得好大機會係4 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af598a92861f24d308f42e1dbab5233f4ff55653","tid":2115164,"uid":308228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T12:56:03.000Z","msg":"一睇就知未入Disk Management度format啦<br />\n一係就自己無做功課   自己塊版唔support就亂咁買M.2"}]}